Class CoGe

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.coge.api.CoGe

  • public class CoGe
extends java.lang.Object
    The workhorse core class to make REST calls againt a CoGe web service and instantiate the various objects.
    Author:
    Sam Hokin

      Construct given just a base URL, like https://genomevolution.org/coge/api/v1/ Used only for calls that don't require authentication.

      Construct given a base URL, username and token, used like https://genomevolution.org/coge/api/v1/stuff/here/and/here?username=x&token=y Used for calls that require authentication.
